e considered when methotrexate is used with other potentially hepatotoxic agents (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/89242/', '', 'Brivaracetam, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Methylphenobarbital, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Tiagabine, Rufinamide, Paramethadione, Perampanel, Ganaxolone, More', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, More', 1767369485);
